metatags.og:title: Arkansas Personal Information Protection Act
metatags.og:description: Arkansas House Bill 1943 (HB 1943), passed in the spring of 2019, became effective in August of 2019. This legislation revises and amends the Arkansas Personal Information Protection Act. Under the revised Arkansas Personal Information Protection Act, the definition of “personal information” has been expanded.
